# Lean Scope

- Do ONLY what was asked. Nothing more.
- No out-of-scope additions, refactors, or "nice to haves".
- No premature abstractions or future-proofing.
- If unclear or ambiguous, ASK — do not assume.
- If unsure whether something is in scope, ASK.
